

=Bio=

"Spanish journalist and researcher at Medialab Prado (Madrid). Passionate supporter of a free and open source journalism and, actually, working to find out how to make it possible. 

Interested in transmedia narratives and, in general, in exploring the resources technology provides journalists with to tell stories in different and exciting ways. No matter how excellent we might be, colective excellency will always be greater."

